Rating: 4
WOW! My entire family RAVED about this all morning long after serving it for Xmas brunch. We used 93/7 lean ground turkey (couldn't find dark meat), but the flavor was still outstanding! One note - recommend you make the sausage mix and then chill for at least an hour or two. Makes the meat much easier to form into patties.